## 2. Introduction

### 2.1 Purpose

This document defines the user acceptance test plan for **{{PROJECT_NAME}}**. It describes the test approach, environment, entry/exit criteria, test cases, and sign-off procedure. Each test case maps one-to-one with a requirement in `docs/SRS.md`.

### 2.2 Scope

**In scope**: all functional requirements (REQ-{{REQ_ID_PREFIX}}-001 through REQ-{{REQ_ID_PREFIX}}-NNN) and non-functional requirements marked as "Must" in SRS-{{PROJECT_NAME}}-001.

**Out of scope**: performance/load testing (covered separately by PERF suite), penetration testing, and infrastructure failover testing unless explicitly listed as UAT requirements.

