## 8. Entry and Exit Criteria

### 8.1 Entry Criteria

- [ ] All SRS requirements at status "Approved"
- [ ] SDD approved by lead Oracle
- [ ] Staging deployment successful (CI green)
- [ ] Test data seeded in staging DB
- [ ] UAT test cases reviewed by Your Name

### 8.2 Exit Criteria

- [ ] All "Must" test cases: pass
- [ ] Zero open P0/P1 defects
- [ ] Accessibility scan: zero WCAG 2.2 AA violations
- [ ] Your Name sign-off recorded in Section 12

