## 10. Suspension and Resumption Criteria

**Suspension**: UAT is suspended if a P0 (system crash / data loss) defect is discovered. Testing resumes after the defect is fixed and the staging environment is re-deployed.

**Resumption**: All previously passed test cases are re-executed for the affected feature area after a P0 fix.

